The collapse tour rolls on. Des Moines thank you for the energy! Absolutely insane couple days. Our van engine exploded yesterday. Started therapy today. My grandmother passed this evening of stage 4 lung cancer. It came all of a sudden and she went fast. Don’t know how I would be getting through this tour without my friends. Thank you to everyone that’s reached out and helped out. STL tomorrow is in honor of Harlene Wills ❤️ 📸: @trapdaddy_trev

Texas it’s so freaking hot 🥵 🫠
📸: @trapdaddy_trev
Cheapsteaks tonight where the music is loud and the steaks are cheap! Dallas Texas let’s kick of @sowhatmusicfest the right way! 🥩 🎥: @trapdaddy_trev

This tour has been so difficult, but also so full filling. There’s nothing I’d rather be doing with my life. The very worst days are always met with incredible nights. The van explosions and inconveniences everyday hardly seem to weigh on my mind every night on stage. Thank you for everyone that’s showed us love on this tour. Thank you to @secretsofficial for taking us out, and thank you @vrsty.nyc for being some of the best friends I could ever ask for. @wearenerv are quickly becoming some of my favorite people as well. Collabs in the works with almost every band on this tour. San Antonio tonight! (Swipe to see me sing pretty) 

New tours announcing soon ☺️

📸: @trapdaddy_trev
I can’t believe this is today! Check the set times! See you on the raceway!

Hitting the road next month with the long time homies in @dropoutkingsaz and our boys in @vrsty.nyc 
(+ @yungmosh + @widow7official)!

Kicking it off with a @vanguardtulsa show and rippin @blueridgerockfest! Can it be September yet?! 🐓
Does this happen to everyone or just me?

Yesterday we got to be the band to kick off @blueridgerockfest! We’ve never had more of our fans in one place before. I can’t believe how many people were singing words I wrote with us. Seeing the crowd get nostalgic for EYHO was real cool too! Very thankful for the opportunity to play American’s largest rock festival! Thank you Blue Ridge! 
Today kicks off the Riot Music tour for us!  We are on the way to Harrisburg now! See you soon HMAC! 

📷: @trapdaddy_trev

Last night was absurd! We got word at midnight on Saturday that there would be a pop-up in Greensboro NC on Sunday. Load in was 10am, so we drove all night to pull up right in time. Show sold out in a matter of minutes, and was insane! From 1PM in the afternoon to 1AM this morning we raged. Shout out to the promoters, @smartpunkrecords, and all the bands that made it happen!

📷: @trapdaddy_trev
No place I’d rather be. 📷: @trapdaddy_trev

Happy shatterday everyone!! This tasty dab was not taken by me but the legendary @sk4ggs from @outlineincolor out of the @dankbangerofficial of some of the best tastiest product I have ever had, PERIOD!! It was an honor to film this and hang with the crew. Please go check out their music today, cause if you don't know, you've been missing out.  Hope you enjoy his vibe and stay lit all!

My mom and sister are being angels and giving my rooster boy a much needed bath while I’m on the road. Can’t wait to be reunited with my flock. Thank you @daddiosaurus and family for taking care of my birds! 🐓 🦆

The Riot Music Tour has come to an end. It was an absolute blast hanging with @dropoutkingsaz & @vrsty.nyc! Can’t wait till the next one, but stoked to get home and see my birds 🐓

📸: @heipphouse_photography

This tour was one for the books! Back in 2019 we took DOK on one of their first runs. It’s been absolutely incredible to see them take off these last few years. I couldn’t be more happy and proud for the whole team. Thank you for running it back with us ❤️. VRSTY have quickly grown to be some of my very best friends (even you @javyleevrsty 🤣). @blueridgerockfest thank you for having us, despite the weather and complications OIC had an amazing set and will not soon forget it. Good luck to VRSTY and DOK on your next tours! Hope to see ya’ll very soon! 🐓❤️

📸
